          <td>1.30 – 1.50 (classic) · 1.20–1.29 (squarer) · 1.51–1.60 (elongated)</td>
          <td>Controls the silhouette. 1.35–1.45 reads “timeless” to most eyes.</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td><strong>Table</strong></td>
