      <li><strong>Pick a metal that supports color goals.</strong> Platinum/white gold for icy; yellow/rose gold for warmth and forgiveness.</li>
      <li><strong>Decide your setting language.</strong> Minimal, Deco, or bold? We’ll sketch multiple directions to visualize the personality.</li>
      <li><strong>Dial the details.</strong> Prongs (double-claws?), shank width, gallery view, hidden halo, engraving, milgrain — small choices define the mood.</li>
    </ol>

